1
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:00,580
This...

2
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:01,940
Let me help you.

3
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:26,450
Divine Lord.

4
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:27,960
It worked.

5
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:28,680
That's great.

6
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,810
The Huangquan Biluo is finally cured.

7
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:31,570
General.

8
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,160
Yunyuan.

9
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:32,640
King Kunmi.

10
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,170
Yunyuan.

11
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:34,820
Why is he like this?

12
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:37,560
He just overused his soul power,

13
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,759
causing his spiritual energy to dry up.

14
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,850
Don't worry.

15
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:41,770
He won't die.

16
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,560
It's just that his cultivation will stop here.

17
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,320
His cultivation will stop here?

18
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,180
How can that be?

19
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,000
What will he do in the future?

20
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,220
Your Highness.

21
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,160
King Kunmi successfully refined the Seven-Colored Stone.

22
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,039
He only damaged his foundation.

23
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:55,039
He cannot advance his cultivation.

24
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,770
It is already the best outcome.

25
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,360
Burning soul fire for nine days and nights

26
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,680
is not something an ordinary person can do.

27
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,720
One slip up,

28
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:04,120
and he would have been reduced to ashes.

29
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,560
You idiot.

30
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,160
Why did you drive me away?

31
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,620
Why did you hide it from me?

32
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,759
If we had done it together,

33
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,440
you wouldn't have damaged your foundation.

34
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,370
Your Highness, stop making a fuss.

35
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,240
If you also damaged your foundation,

36
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,240
and the Heavenly Emperor and Empress blamed us,

37
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,300
I couldn't bear the responsibility.

38
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,920
It was you.

39
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,360
You were hiding it from me, right?

40
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,960
You told Yunyuan the method.

41
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:31,160
I wondered why the usually aloof King Kunmi would personally see you off.

42
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,220
It was at that time.

43
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,940
That's when you two conspired to hide it from me.

44
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,410
Your Highness, this...

45
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,160
I don't know anything.

46
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,160
You!

47
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,480
I have finally succeeded.

48
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,840
So what if it's Fate?

49
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,680
So what if they are gods?

50
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:06,020
My fate is determined by me, not the heavens.

51
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,360
Congratulations, My Lord.

52
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,890
Congratulations, My Lord.

53
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,080
Rise.

54
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:13,920
Lisha.

55
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,560
You did well.

56
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,920
It was all due to My Lord's perfect planning.

57
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,440
I merely executed it.

58
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,520
When I unite the Three Realms,

59
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:25,320
you will be the first under my command.

60
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,020
Thank you for your guidance, My Lord.

61
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:31,360
I have waited ten thousand years for this day.

62
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,100
I actually succeeded.

63
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,640
What a wonderful Human Realm.

64
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,720
We Demons

65
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,840
have stayed in the Demon Realm long enough.

66
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,290
Congratulations, My Lord.

67
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,020
Now, within the Three Realms,

68
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,159
those whose cultivation can match My Lord,

69
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:36,560
are probably only those two.

70
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,120
Have you been to the Human Realm?

71
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,920
I have never been.

72
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,180
I heard from the elders

73
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:45,130
that humans seem very afraid of us.

74
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,520
Hmph.

75
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,440
It's her.

76
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,080
You.

77
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,240
Go check the nearby villages

78
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:25,440
to see if there are any Monster Clan causing trouble.

79
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,760
Yes, My Lord.

80
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,440
Who are you?

81
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,920
Why are you here?

82
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:45,320
I was passing through. I didn't expect to run into monsters.

83
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,159
The ones you just killed.

84
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,650
You saw everything?

85
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,220
Aren't you afraid?

86
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,440
Immortal Sister.

87
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,640
Did you come specifically to kill monsters?

88
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,970
I only kill demons that commit evil crimes

89
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,690
and harm the common people.

90
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,760
Since you are fine,

91
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,090
you should go back soon.

92
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,840
We will meet again, Immortal Sister.

93
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,920
Ah Ran.

94
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,490
Senior Brother.

95
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,409
What are you doing here?

96
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:38,800
You...

97
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:42,120
Did you sneak off to the Human Realm to play again?

98
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,159
I did not.

99
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:47,760
I just went to deliver a little justice.

100
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,850
Senior Brother,

101
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,520
take a look. Is anything missing

102
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,820
from the gift list?

103
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,520
You decide, Senior Brother.

104
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,760
Three months from now is a very auspicious day.

105
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:11,160
Shall we set our wedding for that day?

106
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,600
Okay.

107
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,840
Snake demon!

108
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,039
Run!

109
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,250
Run! It's a monster!

110
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,680
Don't kill me!

111
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,680
It's okay.

112
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:53,080
You're safe now.

113
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,960
Immortal Sister.

114
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,880
Don't be afraid.

115
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,160
It's safe here.

116
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,320
Your injuries aren't serious.

117
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,520
You'll be fully recovered in a few days.

118
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,560
You look so frail, yet you dared to fight a snake demon.

119
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:12,360
That makes you a brave man.

120
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:16,160
I just wanted to save whoever I could.

121
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:19,360
I didn't expect to need you to save me in the end, Immortal Sister.

122
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,620
Protecting the common people is my duty.

123
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,840
Don't worry about it.

124
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,160
By the way,

125
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,040
before the Demon Tribe plunders a village,

126
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:30,720
they always leave traces.

127
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:34,480
But I didn't notice anything unusual before.

128
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:37,820
Why did the snake demon suddenly attack Fu'an Village?

129
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,440
My Lord.

130
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,960
Did you find out?

131
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,760
There is a snake spirit in a cave near Fu'an Village.

132
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,290
However,

133
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:51,360
it has always kept to itself and avoided the villagers.

134
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,960
Kept to itself?

135
00:09:57,520 --> 00:10:00,720
How can a demon be so well-behaved?

136
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,970
Let it have a taste of blood.

137
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:07,160
Understood.

138
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,040
I need to look for clues.

139
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,920
Immortal Sister,

140
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:23,000
your wounds have healed.

141
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,730
Why are you still following me?

142
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:29,440
My chest hurts a little.

143
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,520
Chest pain?

144
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,880
I didn't find any other injuries.

145
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:38,920
I...

146
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:42,080
I just want to follow you, Immortal Sister.

147
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,840
Follow me?

148
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,160
We are not going the same way.

149
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,320
The same way.

150
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,480
I'll go wherever you go.

151
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,760
I've been an orphan since childhood.

152
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,240
Now,

153
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:57,460
the snake demon destroyed my home. I have nowhere to go.

154
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,340
What if I run into monsters again?

155
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:02,880
I'm defenseless. I definitely wouldn't survive.

156
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,360
Immortal Sister,

157
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,560
didn't you say

158
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:08,160
protecting the world is your duty?

159
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,280
I'm a living soul, too.

160
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,170
I need your protection.

161
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:14,840
Fine.

162
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,560
You can follow me for now.

163
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:20,440
We'll find a place to settle you down later.

164
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,960
Whatever you say, Fairy Sister.

165
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,020
My name is Xingran.

166
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,380
Just call me by my name.

167
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:29,040
Then you can call me A-Yin.

168
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,040
A-Yin.

169
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,080
Have you noticed?

170
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,360
The villages we passed recently,

171
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,890
seem to have been plagued by monsters.

172
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,290
But if you look closely,

173
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:12,040
there are no traces left by any monsters.

174
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,920
Could it be

175
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:19,280
that they knew we were coming?

176
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:23,370
But that wouldn't explain why it happens every time.

177
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,240
Fairy Sister,

178
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,440
I'm hungry.

179
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:31,040
Why don't we get something to eat first?

180
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,360
Okay.

181
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:40,360
My Lord.

182
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,890
Where are the monsters?

183
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:52,880
My Lord...

184
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:55,680
I will go find them immediately.

185
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:09,600
A-Ran.

186
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,160
The wedding is approaching.

187
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:12,360
Return immediately.

188
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:24,760
The Demon Tribe again.

189
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,160
Could those villages...

190
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:27,720
Oh no.

191
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:28,760
A-Yin!

192
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,360
A-Yin.

193
00:13:33,760 --> 00:13:34,760
Are you okay?

194
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:35,840
I'm fine.

195
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,680
Look.

196
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,940
I noticed you've lost some weight recently.

197
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:44,100
So I caught some game to help you build up your strength.

198
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,360
What's wrong?

199
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,920
Did something happen?

200
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,120
It was getting late,

201
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,920
and you hadn't come back,

202
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:55,160
so I came out to look for you.

203
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:57,100
You were worried about me.

204
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,680
No.

205
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,810
You were definitely worried about me.

206
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:05,840
I told you I'd keep you safe.

207
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:09,360
This place looks nice.

208
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:12,280
Why don't you settle down here?

209
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,880
Me? Settle here?

210
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,880
What about you?

211
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,160
I have business to attend to.

212
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:18,020
I can't let you follow me anymore.

213
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:19,360
But don't worry.

214
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,880
I'll set up a barrier before I leave.

215
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:25,080
Neither the Monster Tribe nor the Demon Tribe will find this place.

216
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,360
You will be safe.

217
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:27,560
Then...

218
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:31,600
Are you not going to slay monsters and demons anymore?

219
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,720
The things we've encountered lately are too strange.

220
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,220
I need to go back and investigate.

221
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,760
When do you plan to leave?

222
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,160
I'll set up the barrier,

223
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,160
and leave at dawn.

224
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:49,720
Oh.

225
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,860
The Demon Tribe again.

226
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,640
It's you again.

227
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:49,360
Did you plague the nearby villages?

228
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:51,040
Where are the people?

229
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:55,920
I ate them, of course. To increase my cultivation.

230
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,720
You were lucky to escape last time.

231
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:01,320
Today, I will slay you, monster.

232
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:04,320
Hmph. I was careless when you hurt me last time.

233
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,560
You are no match for me now.

234
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,920
Try me.

235
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,319
A-Ran, you're awake.

236
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,740
Are you feeling unwell anywhere?

237
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,520
Who are you, really?
